🎬 CASTING CALL — FEMALE HOST
We’re looking for a female host aged 20–30 to join upcoming content projects.

✨ Who we’re looking for:

— confident and charismatic on-camera presence;

— experience in conversational blogging content or streaming;

— fluent Russian and English;

— ability to travel.

📱 Content formats:

• Instagram Stories / Reels

• Telegram content

• short-form videos

🎥 Responsibilities:

— filming videos based on ready-made scripts;

— hosting and voicing content on camera;

— creating dynamic / sporty / lifestyle / entertainment content.

✨ For more details — DM me directly

